member.example:
The following examples show how to initialize the 
# [XAML](#tab/tabid-1)

 <sfavatar:SfAvatarView AvatarName="Alex"
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center"   
                        HeightRequest="50"
                        CornerRadius="25"
                        WidthRequest="50" />

# [C#](#tab/tabid-2)

 SfAvatarView avatar = new SfAvatarView();
 avatar.AvatarName = "Alex";
 avatar.VerticalOptions = LayoutOptions.Center;
 avatar.HorizontalOptions = LayoutOptions.Center;
 avatar.WidthRequest = 50;
 avatar.HeightRequest = 50;
 avatar.CornerRadius = 25;
 this.Content = avatar;

***

The following example shows how to apply the stroke thickness for a .
# [XAML](#tab/tabid-1)

<avatar:SfAvatarView  AvatarName="Alex"
                      StrokeThickness="10"
                      VerticalOptions="Center"
                      HorizontalOptions="Center"          
                      WidthRequest="150"
                      HeightRequest="150"
                      CornerRadius="75" />

